              "name": "t:names.heading",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p><em><strong>For the days your skin decides to be a little extra. 🌸</strong></em></p><p><em>Blush Flower turns an unexpected skin moment into something a little sweeter. Each box includes 32 flower-shaped hydrocolloid spot patches designed to cover the little spots you’d rather leave alone—while adding a soft, playful detail to your look.</em></p><p><em>Wear one during your morning routine, on a coffee run, to class, or anywhere your day takes you. Because caring for your skin doesn’t always have to look serious, and a not-so-perfect skin day can still be a cute one.</em></p><p><em>And there may be a little surprise waiting inside: select packs include a secret hidden design. Think of it as a tiny bloom picked just for you.</em></p><p><em><strong>Inside the box:</strong></em></p><p><em>32 flower-shaped hydrocolloid spot patches<br/>8 sheets · 4 patches per sheet<br/>A chance to discover a secret hidden design</em></p>",
